Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron karar da aka yi wa Brett Kavanaugh
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar da Brett Kavanaugh ya bayar a gaban kotun koli a ranar Alhamis, da kuma Christine Blasey Ford, matar da ta zarge shi da laifin cin zarafin da aka yi masa a shekarun 1980 a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A halin yanzu, ana ci gaba da nuna rashin amincewar siyasa, inda masu watsa shirye-shirye suka katse watsa shirye-shiryen su na yau da kullum saboda sabon rikicin da aka samu a ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Blake na Arizona ya kulla da FBI na gudanar da bincike na mako guda kan zargin.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi ta shan taba kuma ya yi kokarin cire tufafinsa a wani biki a makarantar sakandare.
A cikin furcinsa na sha'awar, Kavanaugh ya ce yana da tabbacin cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Bisa ga Nielsen, mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli wannan fim din a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya yi lissafin masu kallon tashoshin CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu adadin nan da nan ba ga sauran tashoshin da suka watsa wannan, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen kuma yakan yi wahalar ƙidaya mutanen da suke kallon shirin daga ofishinsa.
Don a ƙara fahimtarsa, wannan taron yana kama da wanda yake kallon wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko kuma bikin Oscar.
Kamfanin Fox News Channel wanda editocinsa suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ya yi gaba da sauran tashoshin da suka samu kimanin 'yan kallo miliyan 5.69 a cikin zaman zaman na tsawon yini, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ce ta biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS tana da miliyan 3.1 da NBC miliyan 2.94 da MSNBC miliyan 2.89 da CNN miliyan 2.52 da suka ce daga Nielsen.
An samu karbuwa sosai bayan an kammala sauraron karar.
Flake shi ne babban jigon wasan kwaikwayon na ranar Juma'a.
Bayan da ofishin wani dan jam'iyyar Republican mai tsaka-tsakin ya fitar da sanarwa cewa zai kada kuri'a a kan Kavanaugh, kyamarorin CNN da CBS sun dauki bidiyon masu zanga-zanga suna ihu a kansa bayan da ya yi kokarin shiga cikin lif don halartar zaman kotun shari'a.
Ya tsaya a tsaye yana kallon su na minti da yawa yayin da ake yi masa ba'a, a yayin da ake watsa shi a CNN.
