Taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara wani taro na neman zabe a garin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin tarurrukan da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da ziyarar da zai kai ga wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da ake jiran kuri'arsa ta cika kujerar da ta ɓace a Kotun Koli, Trump na shirin ƙara yawan goyon baya a zaɓen da ke tafe a tsakiyar wa'adinsa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar asarar iko a kan majalisa bayan zaɓen da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne taron Trump a West Virginia a yau da kuma yadda za a iya kallon shi a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, an shirya shi ne a karfe bakwai na yammacin yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a karkashin bidiyon YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana ne a kan sauraron zaben Burt Kavanaugh a wannan makon wanda ya yi matukar tashin hankali a kan zargin cin zarafin mata, kuma an dage zaben da ake sa ran za a yi a majalisar dattawa har kwana bakwai, har sai FBI ta gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban manufar wannan taron shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su sami nasara a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, kamfen din shugaban kasa Trump ya ce ana gudanar da taron wannan makon ne domin karfafawa masu aikin sa kai da masu goyon bayan jam'iyyar yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai, kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito.
"Sarrafa majalisa na da muhimmanci sosai a ajandar shugaban kasa, kuma zai ziyarci kasashe da dama yayin da muke shiga lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda ya ki bayyana kansa.
An shirya taron a Westbanco Arena a Wheeling, da yammacin yau zai iya tara magoya bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma jan hankalin kafofin watsa labarai a Pittsburgh, kamar yadda West Virginia Metro News ta ruwaito.
A ranar Asabar, Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia karo na biyu a wannan watan, jihar da ya lashe zaben da ya fi kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrissey, dan takarar Senate na jam'iyyar Republican daga West Virginia, wanda ba ya da kyau a cikin kuri'un.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrissey ba cewa shugaban ya zo ne don ya kara masa matsayi a cikin kuri'un, "in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar wani rahoto na Reuters.
