Amurka za ta iya amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa don hana Rasha fitar da makamashinta
Washington na iya "yin amfani da rundunar sojan ruwanta idan ya zama dole" don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha zuwa kasuwannin kasashen waje, ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Ryan Zinke, Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya ce, shigar Rasha cikin Syria, wato, a can, bisa ga umarnin gwamnati, ya zama hujja don gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
