A ranar Laraba ne shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi tsokaci kan wani rahoto da ya fito daga jaridar China Daily a Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa, bayan da ya zargi kasar Sin da tsoma baki a zaben da za a yi ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, wanda China ta musanta.
Trump ya zargi Beijing da kokarin shiga cikin zaben Amurka, kamar yadda jami'an Amurka suka shaida wa Reuters, sabon mataki ne a cikin wani yunkuri da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
Kuma yayin da ya zama al'ada gwamnatocin kasashen waje su yi tallace-tallace don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin yakin cinikayya mai tsanani inda suke karawa juna haraji kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa.
A matsayin maganin, a baya, an yi amfani da harajin da China ta yi a wannan yakin cinikayya a kan masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa da ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na kasar Sin da na Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin kuma tsohon magajin garin Iowa, wanda babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta yi wa ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni barazana.
"China", in ji Branstad a cikin wata sanarwa da aka buga a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register ta ranar Lahadi, "yanzu tana ninka wannan tashin hankali ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace a cikin jaridarmu mai 'yanci".
"A cikin yada farfagandarsu, gwamnatin China ta yi amfani da kyawawan al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da' yancin jarida, ta hanyar sanya talla a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register", Branstad ya rubuta.
"A akasin wannan, a kan kiosk da ke nan a kan titi a Beijing, za ku sami iyakance adadin ra'ayoyi daban-daban kuma ba za ku iya ganin kowane irin gaskiya game da ra'ayoyi daban-daban da mutane a China za su iya yi game da matsalar tattalin arzikin China ba, la'akari da cewa kafofin watsa labarai na kasar Sin suna ƙarƙashin matsin lamba na Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa, "wani daga cikin manyan jaridun kasar Sin ya ki amincewa da buga" labarin, duk da cewa bai bayyana ko wane ne ba.
