An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga birnin Palu bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman abubuwa game da Palu da Donggali, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Sulawesi, wanda ke a ƙarshen bakin tekun a gabar yamma ta tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40 da haihuwar sa sa'ad da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka addabe shi.
Donggala gundumar da ke da nisan fiye da kilomita 300 (180 miles) na gabar tekun arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gundumar da ke da matsayi na ƙasa da lardin, tana da ƙididdigar yawan mutane 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Kamun kifi da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Central Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Ma'adinan nickel ma suna da mahimmanci a lardin, amma galibi suna da yawa a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggali.
Tsunami ya kuma afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996 inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Seismic Ring of Fire kuma ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Waɗannan su ne manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa kasashe 14 inda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: An yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane suka mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke kusa da gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu maso Java, tsibirin Indonesia mafi yawan jama'a, ta jawo tsunami da ya mamaye gabar kudu kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afka wa tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai zurfi ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya na Aceh, inda ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba, kamar yadda ta tunatar da mutane game da mummunan lalacewar girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Ba a yi tsunami a wannan lokacin ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu sa'ad da gine-gine suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine, kuma dubban masu yawon bude ido sun kasance cikin fursuna na ɗan lokaci.
An kama ɗan fari na Sarah Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin cikin gida
An kama Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska da kuma mataimakiyar shugaban kasa, Sarah Palin, bisa zargin kai hari.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga garin Wasilla, a jihar Alaska, bisa zargin aikata laifuka na tashin hankali na cikin gida, hana bayar da rahoto kan tashin hankali na cikin gida, da kuma adawa da kama shi, in ji wani rahoto da hukumar 'yan sanda ta jihar Alaska ta fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, sa'ad da wata abokiyarta ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton laifin da ake zarginsa da shi, sai ya kwace wayarta.
An tsare Palin a cikin sashen tsare-tsaren Mat-Su kuma an sanya masa belin $500, KTU ta ruwaito.
Ya bayyana a kotu ranar Asabar inda ya bayyana cewa "ba shi da laifi", kamar yadda gidan talabijin din ya ruwaito.
Palin yana fuskantar laifuffuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin cewa zai iya fuskantar hukuncin daurin shekara guda a kurkuku da kuma tarar dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin aji B, wanda ke da hukuncin ɗaurin kwana ɗaya a kurkuku da kuma tarar dala dubu biyu.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da aka kai ƙarar laifi a kan Palin ba.
A watan Disamba na shekarar 2017, an tuhume shi da kai wa mahaifinsa hari, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton harin.
Yanzu haka, shari'ar tana gaban kotun dattawa a Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an zarge shi da aikata laifuka na tashin hankali na cikin gida, hana bayar da rahoton tashin hankali na cikin gida, da kuma mallakar makamai a cikin maye da ke da alaƙa da lamarin.
Abokinsa ya ce ya buge ta a fuska.
An soki Sarah Palin a 2016 bayan ta danganta halin zalunci na ɗanta da PTSD bayan hidimarsa a Iraki.
