Masu gabatar da kara a birnin New York na neman a yanke wa Sayful Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci da ya kashe mutane takwas a birnin New York, wanda ba a taba yanke wa wani laifi a jihar ba tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi zargin cewa ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a gefen yammacin Manhattan, inda ya harbe masu tafiya da ƙafa da kuma masu hawan keke da suka tsinci kansu a hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don a ba da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi wa wasu rauni mai tsanani, in ji takardar neman hukuncin kisa da aka shigar a yankin kudancin New York.
A kan waɗannan batutuwa guda biyu, za a iya yanke masa hukuncin kisa, in ji takardar shari'a.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta gurfanar da Saipov a kan tuhuma guda 22 da suka hada da tuhuma guda takwas na kisan kai da kuma cin zarafin mutane, da ake amfani da su a shari'o'in masu aikata laifuka, da kuma na tashin hankali da kuma lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da kuma tunani sosai", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna kwatanta yadda Saipov ya kai harin da "m, mai zalunci da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, lalacewa da kuma asarar rayuka ga iyalan da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erli, Hernán Ferrucci, Hernán Diego Mendoza da Alejandra Damián Pagnucca", in ji takardar da ake nema.
