An kashe Julius da Ethel Rosenberg a shekara ta 1953 a New York, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin laifin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Yakin Cacar Baki, shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenberg da matarsa a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953, a kan kujerar lantarki.
