Ƙungiyar 'yan wasa ta Dundee Stars da Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a raga a wasan da Giants suka yi da Dundee.
Dundee Stars sun rama rashin da suka sha a gasar Elta da Belfast Giants a ranar Juma'a, inda suka ci 5-3 a wasan da suka yi a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
A farkon wasan, Giants sun ci gaba da cin kwallaye biyu da Patrick Dwayne da Francis Beauvillier suka ci.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun kai gida zuwa daidaitawa kafin Dwyer ya dawo da jagorancin Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita wa Dundee kafin Lucas Lunwald Nielsen ya ci biyu ya tabbatar da nasarar.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na uku da kungiyar Adam Keefe ta yi rashin nasara a gasar Elta a kakar wasa ta bana, inda suka zo daga baya suka doke Dundee da ci 2 da 1 a Belfast ranar Juma'a da daddare.
Wannan shi ne karo na hudu da 'yan wasan biyu suka yi kara a kakar wasa, kuma Giants sun ci wasanni uku da suka gabata.
Dwayer ya bude wasan da ci a minti na hudu, 3:35, tare da taimakon Kendall McFaul, yayin da David Rutherford ya taimaka wa Beauvillier kuma ya ninka jagorancin minti hudu bayan haka.
A cikin tashin hankali da aka fara, Sullivan ya dawo da 'yan wasan gida a cikin wasan a cikin minti 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya taimaka wa Cownie don daidaitawa a cikin minti 15.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da jagorancin Giants a farkon hutu tare da ci na biyu a daren a ƙarshen farkon.
